00:08:44.255 --> 00:08:45.359
Mega.

00:08:46.343 --> 00:08:47.783
Duduk.

00:08:50.063 --> 00:08:52.183
Duduk.  Duduk.

00:08:56.983 --> 00:08:59.343
Saya tahu kemarahan Anda beralasan.

00:09:00.983 --> 00:09:03.263
Tapi itu bukan salah Arjun.

